#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:2
msgid "检测参数 2D"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:4
msgid ""
"本章节详细介绍 2D 检测工具（检测项）及其参数含义。每个元件可包含一个或多个检测项；在 **模板编辑器** "
"中选中元件后，可在右侧面板查看并编辑各检测项的参数。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "检测参数总览"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:15
msgid "通用概念"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:17
msgid "在阅读各工具参数前，先了解几个贯穿全篇的通用概念："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:19
msgid ""
"**AI 异常分数**：基于 AI 模型的检测会输出一个 0~1 的异常分数；接近 0 表示与正常样本相似，接近 1 "
"表示差异大。可通过统计图表对比正常 / 异常样本的分数分布，选择合适的判定阈值。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:20
msgid ""
"**颜色范围与有效比例（Valid Ratio）**：基于颜色的检测在 ROI 内用 **HSV 颜色范围** "
"将像素二值化为“有效点”，有效比例定义为 :math:`100 \\times \\dfrac{\\text{有效点数}}{\\text{ROI "
"面积}}`。判定时检查有效比例是否落入设定的 **有效比例范围**。一个 ROI 可配置多组颜色范围，分别独立判定。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:21
msgid ""
"**颜色公式（Color Formula）**：定义如何从像素计算颜色特征。可选 HSV（中心 / 起止色调 + "
"明度范围），或三色公式（Tricolor，如 ``2B-R-G`` 线性组合，配合 X/Y/Z/A 系数与阈值）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:22
msgid "**对齐（Alignment）**：部分检测在判定前先将元件图像与标准样本自动对齐，以消除位置偏移带来的误判。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:23
msgid ""
"**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**：评估后叠加显示二值化 / "
"检测中间结果，便于调参；因有额外计算开销，建议仅在调试阶段开启。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:24
msgid ""
"**使用共享参数（Use Shared Parameters）**：元件加入封装 / "
"料号分组后默认与组内共享参数；关闭后可对该实例单独调参，不再继承分组设置。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:27
msgid "1. 本体检测（Mounting）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:29
msgid "**用途**：检测元件本体的贴装缺陷，包括缺件、错件、损件、偏移、旋转与极性等。ROI 应覆盖元器件主体表面。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "本体检测ROI示例"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:35
msgid "**位置与姿态**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:37
msgid "**旋转角度 (°)（Max Rotation Angle）**：元件本体相对标准姿态的角度偏差；当偏差超过该阈值时判定为 NG。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:38
msgid "**X 偏移 (mm)（Shift X）/ Y 偏移 (mm)（Shift Y）**：样本元件与标准元件本体的平移偏差；超过阈值判 NG。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:40
msgid "**缺陷检测（AI）**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:42
msgid "**常规检测（Significant Defect Check）**：对元件本体的明显缺陷（缺件、错件、方向严重错误等）进行 AI 异常分数判定。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "本体AI分数分布示例"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "本体AI分数分布示例2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:51
msgid ""
"**损件检测（Subtle Defect Check）**：针对本体的破损、缺口等细微异常；检测前先将元件图像与标准样本自动对齐，再以 AI "
"异常分数判定，避免位置偏移导致误判。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "损件检测"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "本体对齐后检测"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "本体对齐后检测2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:63
msgid "**缺件检测（Missing Check）**：判定该位置是否缺少元件。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:64
msgid ""
"**增强缺件检测（Enhanced Missing "
"Check）**：利用对位结果在元件疑似缺失时提前告警；属实验性功能，当对位误判导致误报时可关闭。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:66
msgid "**极性检测（AI，对齐后）**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:68
msgid ""
"**极性检测（Polarity Check）**：判断元件极性方向是否正确。检测前先对齐，并在 **极性 ROI** "
"区域内学习与判定极性特征，以识别极性反转。判定方式同样基于 AI 异常分数。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:69
msgid "**极性检测灵敏度（Polarity Sensitivity）**：调节极性判定的灵敏度；灵敏度越高越容易报出极性异常。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:70
msgid ""
"**极性 ROI（Polarity ROI）**：点击 *设置 ROI* "
"或在显示窗口中直接拖拽，框选用于极性判定的局部区域（通常为极性标识所在处）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "极性检测框"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "极性检测"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "极性检测2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:82
msgid "**其它**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:84
msgid "**启用遮罩（Enable Mask）**：对含有不固定字符 / 图案的区域进行遮蔽，避免其影响 AI 检测。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "遮罩"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:91
msgid "2. 焊料检测 2D（Solder 2D，基于颜色比例）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:93
msgid ""
"**核心思路**：在焊料 ROI 内用 **HSV 颜色范围** 对像素二值化，计算 **有效比例** 并与设定范围比较以判定 OK/NG。一个 "
"ROI 可配置多组颜色范围（如蓝通道斜面焊料、红通道平面焊盘），分别独立设阈值。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "焊料2D ROI"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:99
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:128
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:212
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:238
#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:283
msgid "**参数说明**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:101
msgid ""
"**颜色公式（Color Formula）**：选择 HSV 或三色（Tricolor）公式；选择三色时配置 **三色 X / Y / Z / "
"A** 系数。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:102
msgid "**中心色调（Center Hue）/ 中心饱和度（Center Saturation）**：HSV 模式下色相基准点（位于色盘内部）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:103
msgid "**起始色调（Start Hue）/ 终止色调（End Hue）**：色盘圆环边缘的两点，与中心点共同构成扇形有效色相范围。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:104
msgid "**起始明度（Start Value）/ 终止明度（End Value）**：限定有效像素的明度区间。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:105
msgid "**有效比例范围（Valid Ratio Ranges）**：每组颜色范围对应的有效比例上下限；落入范围内判 OK。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:106
msgid "**有效比例列表（Valid Ratio List）**：评估样本得到的各 ROI 有效比例统计，辅助设定合理范围。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:107
msgid "**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**：显示二值化 Mask 与比例统计（仅建议调试时开启）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "HSV颜色范围挑选"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "多颜色范围示例（蓝/红）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "颜色范围二值化与比例统计"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:120
msgid "3. IC 引脚检测 2D（Lead 2D，AI）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:122
msgid "**用途**：在引脚阵列上自动生成引脚子框，结合 AI 缺陷检测识别桥接、缺焊、虚焊、少锡等。检测框上的三角箭头指向引脚 *外侧*。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "引脚2D(AI)示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:130
msgid "**引脚数量（Lead Count）**：在 ROI 内自动均分生成对应个数的子 ROI。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:131
msgid "**引脚宽度 (mm)（Lead Width）**：匹配实际引脚宽度，使子 ROI 与实体引脚对齐。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:132
msgid "**引脚角度（Lead Angle）**：引脚相对 ROI 的方向角。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:133
msgid "**引脚阈值（Lead Threshold）**：基于每个引脚子 ROI 的 AI 分数判定缺陷。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:134
msgid "**桥接阈值（Bridge Threshold）**：相邻引脚间连锡（短路）的判定阈值。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:135
msgid ""
"**桥接宽度 (mm)（Bridge Width）/ 间隙宽度 (%)（Gap "
"Width）**：定义相邻引脚间桥接检测带的宽度；可按毫米或按引脚间隙百分比设定，居中裁剪以避免引脚边缘干扰。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:136
msgid ""
"**引脚忽略列表（Lead Ignore List）/ 桥接忽略列表（Bridge Ignore List）**：选择不参与检测的引脚 / "
"桥接（从左到右编号，注意特征框角度）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:137
msgid "**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**：显示引脚子框与检测结果。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "引脚2D AI检测示意"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:144
msgid "4. IC 引脚检测 2D v2（Lead 2D v2，基于颜色比例）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:146
msgid ""
"**核心思路**：将引脚区域划分为 **焊料（Solder）/ 焊盘（Pad）/ 引脚尖端（Tip）** "
"三类子区域，分别用颜色范围二值化并计算有效比例，再结合 **均值 / 邻域** 统计对桥接、翘脚（Lifted Lead）等缺陷做鲁棒判定。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:149
msgid "区域划分：上 = **焊盘区（Pad，橙色框）**，下 = **引脚尖端（Tip，红色框）**，中间 = **焊料区（Solder）**。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "V2区域划分与子ROI"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:155
msgid "**通用参数**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "V2通用参数"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:161
msgid ""
"**焊盘长度 (像素)（Pad Length / ext_top）/ 引脚长度 (像素)（Lead Length / "
"ext_bottom）**：沿引脚法线方向向上 / 向下扩展 ROI，使其完整覆盖焊盘与引脚区域。可手动输入或在窗口中拖拽调整。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:162
msgid "**引脚尖端长度 (像素)（Tip Length）**：引脚末端 Tip 子区域的长度。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:163
msgid "**引脚数量（Lead Count）/ 引脚宽度 (mm)（Lead Width）**：在 ROI 内自动均分生成子框并与实体引脚对齐。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:164
msgid "**间隙宽度 (%)（Gap Width）**：相邻引脚间桥接检测带宽度（按间隙百分比），居中裁剪以减少引脚边缘干扰。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:165
msgid "**引脚忽略列表 / 桥接忽略列表**：选择不参与检测的引脚 / 桥接（从左到右编号）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:166
msgid "**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**：显示各子区域二值化结果与比例统计（仅建议调试时开启）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "V2 可视化"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:172
msgid "**焊料 / 焊盘 / 引脚尖端的颜色范围**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "V2焊料参数"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:178
msgid ""
"**焊料颜色范围（Solder Color Range）/ 焊盘颜色范围（Pad Color Range）/ 引脚尖端颜色范围（Tip Color"
" Range）**：分别为三类子区域配置 HSV 或三色颜色公式。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:179
msgid "**焊料 / 焊盘 / 引脚 有效比例范围（Valid Ratio Range）**：各子区域有效比例的 OK 区间。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:180
msgid "**桥接颜色范围（Bridge Color Range）/ 桥接有效比例范围（Bridge Valid Ratio Range）**：用于连锡检测。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "V2焊料色盘"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:186
msgid "**高级设置（Enable Advanced Settings）**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:188
msgid ""
"开启 **启用高级设置（enable_advanced_solder_criteria）** 后，当某引脚的有效比例未落入其 **有效比例范围**"
" 时，会进入二次判定，结合下列阈值降低误报："
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:190
msgid "**焊料平均阈值（Solder Mean Threshold）**：比较该引脚焊料有效比例与所有引脚的平均值；差异大于阈值视为正常。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:191
msgid "**焊料邻域阈值（Solder Neighbor Threshold）**：比较该引脚焊料有效比例与相邻引脚；差异大于阈值视为正常。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:192
msgid ""
"**焊盘平均阈值（Pad Mean Threshold）/ 焊盘邻域阈值（Pad Neighbor Threshold）**：对焊盘区做同样的均值"
" / 邻域比较，用于翘脚判定。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:193
msgid ""
"**最小焊料焊盘差异（Min Solder Pad Difference）**：比较同一引脚的焊料区与焊盘区；正常时焊料 > "
"焊盘，差距过小说明焊盘暴露、焊料不足，可能翘脚。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:194
msgid "**引脚尖端有效比例范围（Tip Valid Ratio Range）**：引脚尖端区域的 OK 比例区间。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:195
msgid ""
"**引脚平均上限阈值（Tip Mean Upper Threshold）/ 平均下限阈值（Tip Mean Lower "
"Threshold）**：所有引脚尖端平均有效比例高于上限或低于下限时判异常。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:198
msgid ""
"判定流程：先检查有效比例是否在 **有效比例范围** 内，若在范围内 ⇒ OK；若超出，则进入二次判定——满足 **平均阈值** 或 "
"**邻域阈值** 任一条件 ⇒ OK，两者都不满足 ⇒ NG。"
msgstr ""

