msgid "V2焊盘参数"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst
msgid "V2 Tip参数"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:208
msgid "5. 桥接检测（Bridge）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:210
msgid "**用途**：独立检测相邻引脚 / 焊点之间的连锡（短路）。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:214
msgid ""
"**桥接颜色公式（Bridge Color Formula）**：选择用于识别连锡的颜色公式（如 ``2B-R-G``）；选择三色时配置 **三色"
" X / Y / Z / A**。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:215
msgid "**值范围（Value Range）**：``2B-R-G`` 等公式的阈值范围（0–100），落入该范围的像素被检出。"
msgstr ""

