#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:250
msgid "9. DIP 桥接检测（DIP Bridge）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:252
msgid "**用途**：检测 DIP 器件相邻引脚 / 焊点之间的连锡。"
