msgid "**焊点数量（Solder Count）/ 焊点宽度 (mm)（Solder Width）**：焊点子框划分。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:258
msgid "**启用可视化（Enable Visualization）**。"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:261
msgid "10. 开焊检测（Open Solder）"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_config_2d.rst:263
msgid "**用途**：检测焊点开路 / 未连接（虚焊、空焊）等缺陷。"
